comments: Hayes (DET) gets to ball height and makes contact to Kuzma's (WAS) hand while it is in contact with the ball, legally blocking the shot.
Kispert (WAS) makes contact with Stewart's (DET) left arm that affects his shot near the rim.
Stewart (DET) legally contests Caldwell-Pope's (WAS) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Cunningham (DET) maintains a legal foot during his spin move.

Replay review of the foul called on Cunningham (DET) pursuant to a coach?s challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Cunningham (DET) makes contact to Kuzma's (WAS) face prior to legally dislodging the ball on his driving shot attempt.
Kuzma (WAS) makes incidental contact with Bey's (DET) right arm after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Satoransky (WAS) makes marginal contact with Stewart (DET) underneath the basket as he jumps to contest the shot attempt near the rim.
Stewart (DET) makes marginal contact with Kuzma (WAS) and then momentarily ties-up the ball in his hands.
Kuzma (WAS) maintains a legal pivot foot.
Hayes (DET) commits a take foul on Satoransky (WAS).
Bey (DET) and Kuzma (WAS) engage and disengage during the free throw attempt, and Kuzma falls after incidental foot-to-foot contact with Bey.
